&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and mentor a team of network automation engineers, providing guidance, support, and professional development opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement a comprehensive network automation strategy aligned with the company’s goals and objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, deploy, and maintain automation solutions for network configuration, monitoring, and management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the execution of network automation projects, ensuring they are delivered on time, within scope, and on budget.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with cross-functional teams to integrate automation solutions with existing network infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and analyze network performance metrics to identify areas for improvement and optimization through automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve complex network issues related to automation and network performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain comprehensive documentation for automation processes, procedures, and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
