&lt;p&gt;NetBrain is seeking a Network Development Engineer with a focus on Automation Deployment to join our Platform team. You will design and implement Python-based automation scripts and frameworks that streamline network operations at enterprise scale. This role sits at the intersection of software development, cloud operations, and real-world network troubleshooting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will build automation that directly reduces high-frequency, high-cost ticket resolution for the world&#39;s largest enterprises and service providers. The challenge here is not scripting for pre-defined problems — it&#39;s designing intelligent automation that adapts to complex, real-world network environments and then validating it actually does what was intended.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
