&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and maintain Python automation scripts and frameworks for network operations use cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, validate, and iterate on automation workflows — confirming scripts achieve intended results at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply cloud and AI tooling knowledge to enhance automation pipelines and deployment practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot network issues and translate them into reusable automation solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the team to improve automation tooling coverage and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;May need to work on customers&#39; platform cases when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
