&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–4 years of Python automation scripting with hands-on automation tools and delivered projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid network troubleshooting skills and foundational understanding of network protocols and architectures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and validating automation workflows: confirming automation behaves correctly at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP) and AI/ML tooling relevant to automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving mindset with attention to validation and production-readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s or Master&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nice to have: Cloud certifications; experience with Ansible, Terraform, or similar; CI/CD pipeline knowledge.&lt;/li&gt;
