&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement comprehensive unit test suites: test design, mocking, fixtures, and edge case coverage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain static analysis tooling and enforce code quality standards across the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to and improve CI/CD pipelines to ensure automated quality gates are effective and reliable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive testing philosophy across the team — from unit tests through integration and regression testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Debug complex issues using systematic, structured debugging approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute Python (primary) and a second language (JavaScript/Node.js preferred) to platform quality initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;May need to work on customers&#39; platform cases when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
