&lt;li&gt;Apply strong software engineering practices: code reviews, design patterns, edge case handling, failure modeling, and production-readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams on integration design and delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;May need to work on customers&#39; platform cases when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
