&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–4 years of hands-on Python development with emphasis on code quality, design patterns, and API design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of networking fundamentals: routing &amp;amp; switching (BGP, OSPF, MPLS, STP, RSTP), QoS, firewall concepts, SD-WAN, and cloud networking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience with API integration design and building production-grade services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle edge cases, failure scenarios, and production concerns with rigor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills; comfortable engaging directly with enterprise customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s or master’s degree in computer science, Information Technology, Electrical Engineering, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nice to have: Networking or Cloud certifications (CCNA, CCNP, AWS, Azure); experience with cloud-native architectures or AI tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
